{"tid":1235851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥會見不同界別人士清楚真誠表達道歉","createTime":"2019-06-17T09:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:10:53.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d459a35d3bdc4e33f589ec438d5a5928bcf9c236","tid":1235851,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"777, 仆街啦你。<br />\n縮係禮賓府見其他人，都唔見市民, 唔見記者, 唔見民主派。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n行政會議成員林正財表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行政長官林鄭月娥今日在禮賓府會面了不同界別人士，包括大學、中小學校長以及宗教人士，林鄭月娥與他見面時，亦清楚及真誠表達道歉</span></span>，他認為特首本人及團隊會深刻反省反思修訂《逃犯條例》引來的風波。林正財說，目前所謂的「暫緩」基本上等於「撤回」，相信政府每用一個字都要作很多考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463417-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463417-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=6e0f3183\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463417-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fb23eae7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463417-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"038fad32ef1e3b2c1dfb05b3e6b98949a5e2c9c5","tid":1235851,"uid":90743,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母扮道歉就慳返<br />\n要你撤回呀依家"},{"pid":"a606cbf6cc0147898d4eb4ff2cd1c20d4d8f4478","tid":1235851,"uid":3077,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"撤回就撤回 暫緩就暫緩<br />\n點樣兩個字係等於呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家中文都唔撚識？"},{"pid":"696c5a3a92cba477de95296d321f75b7b25a6f87","tid":1235851,"uid":76745,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"大學同中小學校長有幫過大家咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"